CatDescriptText: Cutline of related image published in Pittsburgh Courier newspaper February 2, 1946, pg. 25, reads: "Northside Church Quint Clicking - Here's the classy young Bidwell Presbyterian Church A. C. quint, coached by Charles Petty of Western Theological Seminary and managed by Charles E. Bailey, the Courier's Northside representative. The Presbyterians have won two out of their last three games. - Harris Photo."
TitMainTitle: Group portrait of Bidwell Presbyterian Church A. C. basketball team, possibly including coach Charles Petty and manager Charles E. Bailey, posed possibly in Centre Avenue YMCA
